"handle";s:7:"Sheamus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"66";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Curly_Fry";s:4:"text";s:48:"Rayna described whole &quot;chunks&quot; missing";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1426053225";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f9b511";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14260532286";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#eaf712";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1291933;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1291933";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Curly_Fry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"328";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Sheamus";s:4:"text";s:93:"which means the blade will have a narrower profile when reforged, as there&#039;s less metal.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1426053283";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c76b00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14260532806";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c73900";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1291936;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1291936";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Curly_Fry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"328";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Sheamus";s:4:"text";s:429:"the missing shards arent there to be readded to the blade, and if theyre small pieces missing, then the shape can just be hammered down and re formed without the missing metal, into a somewhat lighter weapon. the length will likely stay the same, so you can make the blade thinner, which would make it sharper but more brittle, or reduce the profile, which gives the blade less cleave, but preserves the thickness and durability.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1426053400";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c76b00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14260533975";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c73900";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1291944;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1291944";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Curly_Fry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"328";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Sheamus";